cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea5' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting gNB_name to an invalid string 'invalid_name' will cause a configuration parsing error during startup, preventing the DU from initializing properly due to malformed name.
du.explanation_zh: 將 gNB_name 設定為無效字串 'invalid_name' 會在啟動期間導致配置解析錯誤，由於名稱格式錯誤，阻止 DU 正確初始化。
